LEVEL 2 — Complete/Delete Tasks


Features
* Mark Task as Completed
* Delete Task
* Task Status Display


1️. Mark Task as Completed
Tracks finished tasks.
What it does:
* Uses a flag (true/false)
* Marks task as done


2️. Delete Task
Removes unwanted tasks.
What it does:
* Deletes task from list
* Updates remaining tasks


3️. Task Status Display
Shows which tasks are done or pending.
What it does:
* Prints (Done) beside completed tasks


Summary
Adds task lifecycle management
